Maurice Dorléac https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Dorl%C3%A9ac 0 Georges Maurice Edmond Dorléac (26 March 1901 – 4 December 1979) was a French actor of the stage and screen. He was the father of actresses Catherine Deneuve, Françoise Dorléac and Sylvie Dorléac. Georges_Maurice_Edmond_Dorléac ( 26_March_1901 – 4_December_1979 ) was a_French_actor of the_stage_and_screen .
